survey_response.review_text: Dr Supriya is expert, polite& on time. Charges are also reasonable . The clinic is in a central place and easily  reachable and clean.

I've always been dead scared of doctors n treatments. When I was explained about the need for RCT & wisdom tooth extraction, I thought I would be screaming in pain during treatment. But Dr.Supriya ma'am is everything a great dentist must be. With miraculous ease, top-notch treatment procedures and state of the art equipment, she made sure that I left the clinic with delight. Very peaceful, hygienic clinic. Highly affordable n transparent pricing. One would've never met a doctor with this much patience elsewhere. Very polite, passionate and admirable human. Not all heroes wear capes. She is a superhero in scrubs.

I would definitely recommend The Dental Experts to everyone I know for their dental problems. Dr. Supriya and team are professional in their approach and explain the procedure in detail and transparency maintained at every step that made me trust them.

Dr. Supriya was kind and patient, taking the time to answer all of my questions and explain every step of the procedure. I was also pleased with the results of my cleaning, as my teeth felt incredibly clean. I would highly recommend Dr. Supriya to anyone in need of a dentist.

I would say Dr. Supriya worked magic with my teeth. I have never been to a dentist before and was scared to see one. She is calm , explained the treatment procedure very well performed the RCT and cleaning with very little discomfort. Definitely my go to clinic for all future visits.

Dr. Supriya is very proficient in her work. She is quick to understand your problem and gives the patient sufficient time to help them understand their Dental Treatment. She prioritized my treatment in the best possible way. There's hardly any waiting time at the clinic when you go with an appointment. Thanks to the excellent coordination of the staff. Would definitely recommend her to my friends and family.
